definitions.definition: A minor city in Hardin County , Iowa , United States .
A neighbourhood of Lexington , Fayette County , Kentucky , United States .
A town and former borough in the Metropolitan Borough of Bury , Greater Manchester , England ( OS grid ref SD7807 ) .
A hamlet (formerly a colliery village, now demolished) in Amble parish and Hauxley parish, Northumberland , England ( OS grid ref NU2602 ) .
